---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Reviews
description: In-depth game reviews with clear verdicts from The Patch.
category: reviews
pagination:
  data: collections.reviews
  size: 12
  alias: posts
permalink: "/reviews/{% if pagination.pageNumber > 0 %}page/{{ pagination.pageNumber }}/{% endif %}"
---
<header class="page-header">
  <div class="wrap">
    <span class="badge badge-reviews">reviews</span>
    <h1>Reviews</h1>
    <p style="color:var(--paper-dim);">Every review ships with a Verdict Patch — a clear score and a plain-English breakdown of what's good and what's not.</p>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="section" style="border-bottom:none;">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="grid">
      {% for post in posts %}
      {% include "partials/card.njk" %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
